# Requirement
###gcc --version
[tcn@localhost gcov]$ gcc --version
gcc (GCC) 8.3.1 20191121 (Red Hat 8.3.1-5)

###lcov version
[tcn@localhost gcov]$ lcov -v
lcov: LCOV version 1.14

#build
make gcov  #to build img & run, then get the html report by lcov

